54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 664.2 Td (Your business structure determines how you pay taxes, your personal liability,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 650.2 Td (and how much paperwork you deal with. Get this right early -- changing later) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (is expensive and complicated.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 606.4 Td (Sole Proprietorship vs LLC vs S-Corp: Comparison) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 574.6 Td (SOLE PROPRIETORSHIP) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.6 Td (- Cost to form: $0 \(just start working\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (- Personal liability: UNLIMITED - your personal assets are at risk) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (- Taxes: Report on Schedule C of personal return) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (- Self-employment tax: 15.3% on ALL net profit) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 502.6 Td (- Complexity: Lowest - no state filings required) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 488.6 Td (- Best for: Side hustles under $20K/year, testing a business idea) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 460.8 Td (LLC \(Limited Liability Company\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (- Cost to form: $50-$500 depending on state) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (- Personal liability: LIMITED - business assets are separate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 416.8 Td (- Taxes: Default pass-through \(Schedule C\) or elect S-Corp) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 402.8 Td (- Self-employment tax: 15.3% on net profit \(unless S-Corp election\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 388.8 Td (- Complexity: Moderate - annual state filings, operating agreement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 374.8 Td (- Best for: Any business earning $5K+/year or with liability risk) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 347.0 Td (S-CORPORATION \(S-Corp Election\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 331.0 Td (- Cost to form: LLC cost + $0 to file Form 2553 with IRS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 317.0 Td (- Personal liability: LIMITED) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 303.0 Td (- Taxes: Pay yourself a 'reasonable salary' + take distributions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 289.0 Td (- Self-employment tax: Only on salary portion \(not distributions\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 275.0 Td (- Complexity: Highest - payroll, corporate tax return \(Form 1120S\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 261.0 Td (- Best for: Businesses netting $50K+ profit after expenses) Tj ET
