BT /F1 10 Tf 54 105.4 Td (Best If Revenue    | Under $20K   | $5K-$50K     | Over $50K) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 91.4 Td (Complexity Level   | Very Low     | Low-Medium   | High) Tj ET
