BT /F1 10 Tf 54 159.6 Td (Below that, the extra costs \(payroll service, corporate tax return\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 145.6 Td (eat up the savings. Above that, savings grow with every dollar.) Tj ET
