BT /F2 12 Tf 54 624.4 Td (Step-by-Step LLC Formation Checklist \(10 Steps\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.6 Td (- STEP 1: Choose your state of formation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.6 Td (   Most people should form in the state where they live/operate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.8 Td (- STEP 2: Choose your LLC name) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.8 Td (   Must include 'LLC' or 'Limited Liability Company.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.8 Td (   Search your state's business database to confirm availability.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.8 Td (   Check domain name availability and social media handles.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 493.0 Td (- STEP 3: Designate a registered agent) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 479.0 Td (   This is the person/company that receives legal mail for your LLC.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 465.0 Td (   You can be your own agent \(free\) or use a service \($50-$300/year\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 441.2 Td (- STEP 4: File Articles of Organization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 427.2 Td (   Submit to your Secretary of State \(online in most states\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 413.2 Td (   Processing time: 1-10 business days \(expedited available\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 389.4 Td (- STEP 5: Get your EIN \(Employer Identification Number\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 375.4 Td (   Free from IRS.gov - takes 5 minutes online.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 361.4 Td (   You need this for bank accounts, hiring, and tax filing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 337.6 Td (- STEP 6: Create your Operating Agreement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 323.6 Td (   Required in some states, recommended in ALL states.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 309.6 Td (   Defines ownership percentages, profit distribution, and decision-making.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285.8 Td (- STEP 7: Open a business bank account) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 271.8 Td (   Bring your Articles of Organization, EIN letter, and photo ID.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 248.0 Td (- STEP 8: Get required licenses and permits) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 234.0 Td (   Check city, county, and state requirements for your industry.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 210.2 Td (- STEP 9: Set up your bookkeeping system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 196.2 Td (   Start tracking income and expenses from Day 1 \(see Chapter 4\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 172.4 Td (- STEP 10: Understand your tax obligations) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 158.4 Td (   Register for state/local taxes if required. Set up quarterly payments.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 128.6 Td (Registered Agent: Explained) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 100.8 Td (A registered agent receives legal and government documents on behalf) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 86.8 Td (of your LLC. Every LLC must have one.) Tj ET
