54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Why Separate Personal and Business Accounts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (This is NON-NEGOTIABLE. Mixing personal and business money:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.6 Td (- Destroys your liability protection \(courts can 'pierce the corporate veil'\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.6 Td (- Makes tax time a nightmare \(sorting transactions = hours of wasted time\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.6 Td (- Triggers IRS red flags during audits) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.6 Td (- Makes it impossible to know if your business is actually profitable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.6 Td (- Prevents you from getting business loans or credit) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.8 Td (THE RULE: Every dollar in, every dollar out goes through your business account.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.8 Td (Pay yourself a regular 'owner's draw' transfer to your personal account.) Tj ET
