BT /F1 10 Tf 54 411.4 Td (- Many banks charge $10-$30/month for business checking) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 397.4 Td (- Some waive fees with minimum balance \($1,500-$5,000\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 383.4 Td (- Online banks \(Relay, Mercury, Novo\) often have $0 monthly fees) Tj ET
