BT /F1 10 Tf 54 339.6 Td (- Some banks limit free transactions \(200-500/month\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 325.6 Td (- Excess transactions may cost $0.25-$0.50 each) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 311.6 Td (- Consider your expected volume when choosing) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 283.8 Td (FACTOR 3: Integration) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 267.8 Td (- Does it connect to QuickBooks, Wave, or your accounting software?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 253.8 Td (- Does it offer Zelle, ACH transfers, or wire capabilities?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 239.8 Td (- Can you deposit checks via mobile app?) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 212.0 Td (FACTOR 4: Cash Deposits) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 196.0 Td (- If you handle cash, you need a bank with local branches) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 182.0 Td (- Online-only banks cannot accept cash deposits) Tj ET
