BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (CHAPTER 3: TAX ESSENTIALS FOR NEW BUSINESSES) Tj ET
54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 664.2 Td (Taxes are the #1 reason new business owners get in trouble. This chapter) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 650.2 Td (gives you a clear system so you never face a surprise tax bill again.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 620.4 Td (Business Tax Types Explained) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 588.6 Td (1. FEDERAL INCOME TAX) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.6 Td (- What: Tax on your business profits \(revenue minus expenses\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.6 Td (- Rate: Your personal tax bracket \(10%-37% depending on total income\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (- When: Filed with personal return by April 15) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (- Form: Schedule C \(sole prop/single-member LLC\) or Form 1120S \(S-Corp\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (2. SELF-EMPLOYMENT TAX) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (- What: Social Security \(12.4%\) + Medicare \(2.9%\) = 15.3%) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (- Who pays: All sole proprietors and LLC members) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (- Calculated on: Net profit from Schedule C) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (- Note: Employees split this with their employer. You pay BOTH halves.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (- Silver lining: You can deduct 50% of SE tax on your 1040) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 403.0 Td (3. STATE INCOME TAX) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (- What: State-level tax on business income) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (- Rate: Varies by state \(0% in TX, FL, WY, NV, SD, WA, AK, NH, TN\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.0 Td (- Note: Some states have separate business taxes \(CA franchise tax = $800 min\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 331.2 Td (4. SALES TAX) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (- What: Tax collected from customers on taxable goods/services) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.2 Td (- Rate: Varies by state and locality \(0%-10%+\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 287.2 Td (- Your role: Collect from customers, then remit to state \(monthly/quarterly\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 273.2 Td (- Register: Get a sales tax permit from your state's revenue department) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 259.2 Td (- Note: Most services are NOT subject to sales tax \(check your state\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 231.4 Td (5. QUARTERLY ESTIMATED TAX PAYMENTS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 215.4 Td (- What: Prepayments toward your annual tax bill) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 201.4 Td (- Who: Anyone expecting to owe $1,000+ in taxes for the year) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 187.4 Td (- Penalty: Underpayment penalty if you don't pay quarterly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 173.4 Td (- Amount: Roughly 25-30% of net profit each quarter) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 143.6 Td (Quarterly Estimated Tax Payment Schedule) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 115.8 Td (The IRS requires quarterly payments. Miss these and you pay penalties.) Tj ET
endstream
