BT /F1 10 Tf 54 375.0 Td (   Late fee: 1.5% per month on overdue invoices) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 351.2 Td (- 3. TIMELINE & DEADLINES - When you will deliver each milestone) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 337.2 Td (   Include: 'Timeline assumes client provides feedback within X days') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 313.4 Td (- 4. REVISION POLICY - How many rounds included, cost of extras) Tj ET
