BT /F1 10 Tf 54 223.8 Td (   Include: Kill fee \(25-50% of remaining balance\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 200.0 Td (- 7. CONFIDENTIALITY - Both sides keep business info private) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 186.0 Td (   Protects your processes AND their business information) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 162.2 Td (- 8. LIABILITY LIMITATION - Cap your exposure) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 148.2 Td (   Standard: 'Liability limited to total fees paid under this agreement') Tj ET
