BT /F1 10 Tf 54 110.4 Td (   Covers: Natural disasters, pandemics, government actions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 86.6 Td (- 10. DISPUTE RESOLUTION - How to handle disagreements) Tj ET
