BT /F2 12 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Non-Disclosure Agreement \(NDA\) Overview) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.4 Td (An NDA protects confidential information shared between parties.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 634.6 Td (WHEN YOU NEED AN NDA:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (- Before discussing proprietary business ideas with potential partners) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.6 Td (- When hiring contractors who will access sensitive information) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.6 Td (- When a client shares confidential business data with you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.6 Td (- Before sharing your trade secrets with potential investors) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 548.8 Td (KEY NDA ELEMENTS:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.8 Td (- Definition of confidential information \(be specific\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.8 Td (- Obligations of receiving party \(must protect, cannot share\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 504.8 Td (- Exclusions \(public info, independently developed info\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 490.8 Td (- Term/duration \(typically 2-5 years\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 476.8 Td (- Remedies for breach \(injunctive relief, damages\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 453.0 Td (TIP: Use mutual NDAs \(both sides are bound\) whenever possible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 439.0 Td (One-sided NDAs where only you are restricted can be unfair.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 409.2 Td (Terms of Service Basics) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 381.4 Td (If you have a website or sell online, you need Terms of Service \(ToS\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.6 Td (- Acceptable use policy \(what users can/cannot do\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.6 Td (- Intellectual property rights \(your content is protected\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.6 Td (- Limitation of liability \(limit your legal exposure\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.6 Td (- Disclaimer of warranties \(no guarantees of specific results\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.6 Td (- Refund/return policy \(be clear and specific\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 287.6 Td (- Privacy policy \(required by law if you collect any data\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 273.6 Td (- Governing law \(which state's laws apply\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 249.8 Td (TOOLS: Termly.io \($15/mo\) and TermsFeed generate compliant policies.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 235.8 Td (For custom terms, budget $500-$1,500 for an attorney.) Tj ET
