BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (They work only for you      | Multiple clients) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.2 Td (You provide training        | Already skilled) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.2 Td (Paid hourly/salary          | Paid per project) Tj ET
