BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.2 Td (- 50% due upon completion/delivery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.2 Td (- Best for: Projects under $5,000) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 335.4 Td (Option B - MILESTONE-BASED \(Best for Large Projects\)) Tj ET
