BT /F1 10 Tf 54 293.4 Td (- 25% at second milestone \(e.g., revisions complete\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 279.4 Td (- 25% at final delivery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 265.4 Td (- Best for: Projects over $5,000) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.6 Td (Option C - RETAINER \(Best for Ongoing Relationships\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 227.6 Td (- Client pays fixed monthly fee in advance \(due 1st of month\)) Tj ET
