BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185.6 Td (- Best for: Marketing, consulting, maintenance services) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 161.8 Td (Option D - PAY IN FULL UPFRONT \(Best for Products/Low-Touch Services\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 147.8 Td (- Full payment before delivery) Tj ET
