BT /F1 10 Tf 54 293.0 Td (- 1. Spending money before making money \(fancy logos, website, office\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 279.0 Td (   FIX: Get paying customers first. Invest profits back into the business.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 255.2 Td (- 2. Not tracking finances from Day 1) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.2 Td (   FIX: Set up bookkeeping the same day you form your LLC.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 217.4 Td (- 3. Trying to serve everyone instead of a specific niche) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 203.4 Td (   FIX: Pick one ideal customer. You can expand later.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 179.6 Td (- 4. Underpricing to 'get experience') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 165.6 Td (   FIX: Charge at least 80% of market rate from Day 1. Add bonuses for value.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 141.8 Td (- 5. Not having a contract before starting work) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 127.8 Td (   FIX: No signature, no work. Protect yourself legally.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 104.0 Td (- 6. Ignoring marketing until you 'need' clients) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 90.0 Td (   FIX: Market consistently even when busy. Pipeline delays are real.) Tj ET
